data.description: Seller offering $5K in Sellers Concessions with acceptable offer!!!!  With Winter coming soon Seller is highly motivated and has authorized a price reduction. Discover your perfect Alaskan retreat! This thoughtfully remodeled Single Family ranch-style home offers 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, and a convenient 1-car garage. Nestled on a sprawling 1.1-acre lot, this property provides ample space for your dreams to flourish. With 1,220 sq ft of living space and a 264 sq ft garage, there's room to spread out and enjoy every inch of this charming home. Built with quality in mind, the 2x6 construction and 3-tab shingled roof provide lasting durability. Step inside to a modern oasis featuring luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring that's both stylish and easy to maintain. The heart of the home is adorned with butcher block countertops, adding warmth to the space. The fully equipped kitchen invites culinary creativity. Efficiency meets comfort with baseboard radiant heating powered by an oil-fired furnace, ensuring cozy warmth during colder months. The home is complete with a washer and dryer for added convenience. Embrace the tranquility of private living with a dedicated well and sewer system. This well-maintained property offers the serenity you've been seeking. Originally built in 1977 and fully remodeled in 2021, this home seamlessly blends timeless design with contemporary upgrades. All appliances are included, allowing for a seamless move-in experience. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of Alaskan paradise. Welcome home!
